text: THIS AGREEMENT sets forth the terms and conditions agreed to between Chase Bank USA, N.A. ("Chase") and you as an "Affiliate" in the Chase Affiliate Program.
Last Updated: April 6, 2007
Chase will pay Affiliate a fee for each approved credit card account that originates from a link in Affiliate’s Website.
For purposes of determining Affiliate’s Commission, an "Approved Account" means any Chase credit card application that is approved by Chase.
The term of this Agreement will commence on the date that the Affiliate Registration Form is approved by Chase.
This Agreement will be governed in all respects by the laws of the State of Delaware.
The total payment shall be USD 10,000 payable within 30 days.
An advance of INR 75,000 must be paid before execution.
